         </properties>
         <data>'Quote Valid for 30 days
Please note that this estimate does not include engineer parking.
This will also be invoiced at cost.'</data>
      </text-field>
      <container>
         <properties>
            <height>1cm</height>
            <left>0cm</left>
            <top>1.5cm</top>
            <width>18.5cm</width>
         </properties>
         <text-field>
            <properties>
               <color>#343738</color>
               <font-size>6pt</font-size>
               <height>1cm</height>
               <hyphenate>true</hyphenate>
               <left>0cm</left>
               <text-align>left</text-align>
               <top>0cm</top>
               <white-space-collapse>true</white-space-collapse>
               <width>18.5cm</width>
            </properties>
            <data>'This is a quote only and is subject to change following an inspection of the site and equipment. In particular, this is not an offer to provide the relevant services/goods at the amounts quoted. This quote is subject 
to our terms and conditions which are available at www.jla.com/legal/ .If you decide not to proceed with this quote, an invoice will follow shortly for work already completed. Please also note that should you need 
to cancel any parts after they have been ordered, there may be a re-stocking fee payable by you, the customer.'</data>
         </text-field>
      </container>
